<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ وَقَفَ عَلَى جَمَاعَةٍ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> يُمْكِنُ حَصْرُهُمْ:</span> وَجَبَ تَعْمِيمُهُمْ وَالتَّسْوِيَةُ بَيْنَهُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِلَّا:</span> جَازَ التَّفْضِيلُ <span class="c2">(١)</span>، وَالاقْتِصَارُ عَلَى وَاحِدٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَالهِبَةُ مُسْتَحَبَّةٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَيَصِحُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> هِبَةُ:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- مُصْحَفٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَكُلِّ مَا يَصِحُّ بَيْعُهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتَنْعَقِدُ:</span> بِمَا يَدُلُّ عَلَيْهَا عُرْفاً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتَلْزَمُ:</span> بِقَبْضٍ، بِإِذْنِ وَاهِبٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَمَنْ أَبْرَأَ غَرِيمَهُ مِنْ دَيْنِهِ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>: بَرِئَ، وَلَوْ لَمْ يَقْبَلْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَيَجِبُ تَعْدِيلٌ فِي عَطِيَّةِ وَارِثٍ؛ بِأَنْ يُعْطِيَ كُلًّا بِقَدْرِ إِرْثِهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ فَضَّلَ:</span> سَوَّى بِرُجُوع.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (أ) و (ج): التعميم.<br>(٢) في (د): وتصح.<br>(٣) قوله: (من دينه) سقطت من (ب).</p> </div>